- Move the mouse cursor over a name to see more information.
- Click on a name to go to the corresponding page.
- The arrows of the inheritance tree are

a.title: ― InstanceKey: Single-valued key representation produced from the merge of the representations of all key members and a descriptor.
a.xlink:title: ― InstanceKey: Single-valued key representation produced from the merge of the representations of all key members and a descriptor.

a.title: ― SubstantiveValueDomain: Value domain for a substantive conceptual domain. Typically a description and/or enumeration of allowed values of interest.
a.xlink:title: ― SubstantiveValueDomain: Value domain for a substantive conceptual domain. Typically a description and/or enumeration of allowed values of interest.

a.title: ― ContextualComponent: Encapsulates contextual information of the key-value datastore to provide a scope to the instance key. The instance key is unique within the scope.
a.xlink:title: ― ContextualComponent: Encapsulates contextual information of the key-value datastore to provide a scope to the instance key. The instance key is unique within the scope.

a.title: ― IdentifierComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a long or wide data structure to identify the units associated to data points, and in dimensional and key value data structures to provide identifying fields for the instance values.
a.xlink:title: ― IdentifierComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a long or wide data structure to identify the units associated to data points, and in dimensional and key value data structures to provide identifying fields for the instance values.

a.title: ― SyntheticIdComponent: Persistent and unique identifier (PIDs) to provide standarized, long-lasting identification.
a.xlink:title: ― SyntheticIdComponent: Persistent and unique identifier (PIDs) to provide standarized, long-lasting identification.

a.title: ― DimensionComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a dimensional data structure to identify the universes associated with data points. The variable acts as a field in the compound identifier (the key structure) to disambiguate the cells in the multi-dimensional "cube".
a.xlink:title: ― DimensionComponent: Role given to a represented variable in the context of a dimensional data structure to identify the universes associated with data points. The variable acts as a field in the compound identifier (the key structure) to disambiguate the cells in the multi-dimensional "cube".

a.title: ― KeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a key.
a.xlink:title: ― KeyMember: Single data instance that is part of a key.

a.title: ― DataPoint: Container for an instance value.
a.xlink:title: ― DataPoint: Container for an instance value.

a.title: ― ValueDomain: Set of permissible values for a variable (adapted from ISO/IEC 11179).
a.xlink:title: ― ValueDomain: Set of permissible values for a variable (adapted from ISO/IEC 11179).

a.title: ― InstanceValue: Single data instance corresponding to a concept (with a notion of equality defined) being observed, captured, or derived.
a.xlink:title: ― InstanceValue: Single data instance corresponding to a concept (with a notion of equality defined) being observed, captured, or derived.

a.title: ― TypedString: TypedString combines a type with content defined as a simple string. May be used wherever a simple string needs to support a type definition to clarify its content.
a.xlink:title: ― TypedString: TypedString combines a type with content defined as a simple string. May be used wherever a simple string needs to support a type definition to clarify its content.

a.title: ― Identifier: Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.
a.xlink:title: ― Identifier: Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.

a.title: ― WhiteSpaceRule: WhiteSpace constrains the value space of types derived from string.
a.xlink:title: ― WhiteSpaceRule: WhiteSpace constrains the value space of types derived from string.

a.title: ― Datum: Correspondence of a data instance to the concept it represents.
a.xlink:title: ― Datum: Correspondence of a data instance to the concept it represents.
